{"tid":2004670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★美華裔教授研究新冠病毒　「即將有重大發現」前遭槍殺","createTime":"2020-05-06T14:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T17:41:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6d5fb4eebd48622926e7ce49689d81a31eb6ce96","tid":2004670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:51:00.000Z","msg":"美國賓夕法尼亞州匹茲堡大學（University of Pittsburgh）37歲的醫學院助理教授劉彬（Bing Liu，譯音）上周六（5月2日）在家中遭槍殺，兇徒其後被發現懷疑吞槍自殺；匹茲堡大學醫學院發文悼念劉彬，指他生前致力研究新型冠狀病毒肺炎（COVID-19），且即將有重大突破，詎料突遭遇橫禍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4438624/org/87f99bc55783787f69fa7111822135de.jpg/bKjCNEa7IiIVbnvjEDfLKLTph8gSUBeXXpwOZV6cDmU?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4438624%2Forg%2F87f99bc55783787f69fa7111822135de.jpg%2FbKjCNEa7IiIVbnvjEDfLKLTph8gSUBeXXpwOZV6cDmU%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=71369348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉彬當日是在羅斯鎮（Ross Township）的寓所中遇害，警方到場發現其頭、頸及身體上均有足以致命的槍傷；及後當局在劉彬寓所附近的一輛汽車上發現另一具男屍，初步相信是兇手，且認識劉彬，暫無其他人士涉案；當局懷疑兇手在殺害劉彬後返回車上自殺，現正調查其犯案動機。<br />\n<br />\n匹茲堡大學醫學院網站發表悼文稱，劉彬在研究新型冠狀病毒的感染機制及併發症方面「即將有非常重大的發現，我們將努力完成他的研究，以向其傑出的科學成就致敬，全體科學界都將為他的離世而哀悼。」<br />\n<br />\n大學網站資料顯示，劉彬早年於新加坡國立大學取得電腦科學學士及博士學位，後來於卡內基美隆大學（Carnegie Mellon University）進行博士後研究，現為匹茲堡大學醫學院計算與系統生物學系（Computational &amp; Systems Biology）的研究助理教授。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/469492/%E7%BE%8E%E8%8F%AF%E8%A3%94%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88bing-liu%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%89%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE-%E5%89%8D%E9%81%AD%E6%A7%8D%E6%AE%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F469492%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25A3%2594%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588bing-liu%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE-%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%25AE%25BA&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=7c899e03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/469492/%E7%BE%8E%E8%8F%AF%E8%A3%94%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88bing-liu%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%89%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE-%E5%89%8D%E9%81%AD%E6%A7%8D%E6%AE%BA</a>"},{"pid":"63872e975051034f2332ccb6516d820ae165d3da","tid":2004670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf0fa078dd8212ce654dae64fb004efcf230e3b","tid":2004670,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />荷里活電影劇情"},{"pid":"610b5b7e1b08ad9e61f2c71ad2052804872f5c5e","tid":2004670,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"549223b76c763047a692ca49542911e478584bda","tid":2004670,"uid":296056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔信啲時間咁巧合"}